## Style Roadmap

### MVP

- `styleType: 'petory'` — Petory Style, fixed default, no picker

### Later Versions (planned — keep in schema & docs)

| `styleType` | Name | Notes |
|-------------|------|-------|
| `petory` | Petory Style | MVP default |
| `pixel` | Pixel | Retro pixel-art |
| `sticker` | Sticker | Flat sticker look |
| `plush` | Plush | Soft doll texture |
| `clay` | Clay | Clay / craft look |
| `cyber` | Cyber Pet | Sci-fi / neon |

- Each later style gets its own MiniMax prompt variant (extend base prompt)
- Style picker page returns when multi-style ships — do not delete style types from codebase
- MVP: skip picker UI; always generate with Petory Style prompt
